VAR __Count = 54

VAR __Min = MIN('brand_health'[ppa])

VAR __Max = MAX('brand_health'[ppa])

VAR __Difference = (__Max - __Min)

VAR __Size = IF(__Difference > 0, __Difference / __Count, 1)

VAR __BinNumber = INT(('brand_health'[ppa] - __Min) / __Size)

RETURN
	IF(
		ISBLANK('brand_health'[ppa]),
		BLANK(),
		__Min + (MIN(__BinNumber, __Count - 1) * __Size)
	)
